The paper proposes a deep neural network model for generating 3D caricatures from face photos, which involves computer graphics (cs.GR) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The authors also mention the use of a large dataset and PCA model, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the authors conduct user studies and introduce an interactive control, which suggests a focus on human-computer interaction and machine learning (cs.LG).
